Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:46.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:57.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:05.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:11.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:18.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:22.43,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:32.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:39.51,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:46.26,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:57.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:05.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:46.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在傷害別人之前　不必強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:57.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說著她低下頭　在黑夜裡哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:05.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷黏合在一起　渾身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:11.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停　卻沒有傘來遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:18.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:22.43,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰鬥才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:32.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的彼岸所見到的　是五彩光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:39.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那時蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:46.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　雖說不能像鳥兒一樣自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:57.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害別人之後的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:05.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地閉上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}#18  交錯的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距反聯邦勢力史無前例的大型恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Break Pillar」已經過去了4個月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量被害者及其家屬的悲痛尚未平息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:15.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}非洲塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是幸於Memento Mori而避免了軌道電梯的完全破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為剝落的外壁造成的異常氣象也開始恢復正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今天  人類迎來了嶄新的復興之日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑藉各聯邦加盟國的技術支援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲塔再次開始輸電
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值此大喜之日  我作為首任地球聯邦總統在此宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著復興  新的戰鬥也將從今天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了預防大型恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:01:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯邦軍將指揮權轉交給獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了剿滅反聯邦勢力  實現新的統一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們全力以赴地奮戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒發現馬內金上校的行蹤嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然保安局已經在增援了  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你說Celestial Being在宇宙裡出現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是赤道環上的Memento Mori 2號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來開路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是A-LAWS  防守如此堅固
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞  去掩護她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅動系統的控制如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就幫他們這一次  如果是為了破壞衛星兵器的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being把衛星兵器幹掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來A-LAWS把注意力都集中到宇宙裡去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們的搜索也會放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此為機會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開飯！開飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  簡直沒一點規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做好了  別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來幫忙分發食物！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個藏身之所能待多久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為軌道電梯那件事  戰力損失嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重整旗鼓之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的監視越來越嚴了  這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也不是萬能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不採取行動的話就不會有任何改變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕  克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們像是在一個無法逃離的浪潮中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:38.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}なくす事が拾うためなら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:43.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}別れるのは出逢うため
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:49.28,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「さようなら」のあとには　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:55.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「こんにちは」と出逢うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}緑色芝生…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:38.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}若丟棄是為了撿回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:43.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}那分別就是為了相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:49.28,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}告別之後　一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:55.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}迎來重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}想躺在那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌是…瑪麗娜那首？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼廣播裡會放這首歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說幾次  不許這麼叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蘇摩·佩麗絲  超人機關的超兵1號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上  上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校——！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？  為什麼上校會死？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架GN-X  是安德烈少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他殺的嗎？  自己的親人  自己的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  我是蘇摩  蘇摩·佩麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要卻得不到的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼簡單就捨棄了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明向上校發誓不再讓她戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時先靜一靜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理心緒是需要時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是讓她遇上危險的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己先冷靜地想一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重視她的話就去理解一下  她想要戰鬥的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲是否也是一樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去家人的悲傷變成憎恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該對露易絲說些什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以肩膀的傷口為中心有細胞的再生障礙正在擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擬GN粒子的影響…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是其症狀比較輕微
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟拉塞的情況幾乎完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能認為有什麼在起著抑制作用…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候  如果能夠與吠陀連接的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯  不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要得到OO的改革者的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  對方沒有Twin-Drive的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王牌就是我的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being再次開始活動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在也是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說  我對現在的情況感到灰心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰心？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報控制和增強軍備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把舊世代的做法擴散到世界規模而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來準備怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類沒有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說總有一天所有的人類都會成為改革者嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時代的變革期必須捨棄那些陳舊和邪惡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說那些理所當然般地擁有財富或者權利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同類之上俯視大眾的那些舊世代的思考方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在說我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是否願意都會被時代甩在後面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你的美貌會隨時間一起逝去一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拘泥於那華美的過去  通過傷害他人而獲得安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道是錯誤的卻欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得需要有人來告誡他們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的價值觀太過狹隘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在考慮用更廣泛的視野來看待這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那我期待著你所說的廣泛的世界的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我可以先說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無法成為改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很可悲  但這就是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？  到現在把她推到一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經沒有利用價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不交給你來照看？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這四個月裡你不是經常和她見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想聽Celestial Being的情報而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就當是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你晉升為中尉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經查明\N在「Break Pillar」事件裡我擊墜的機體是政變主謀搭乘的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且也得到了上層的賞識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會被你祝賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死親生父親然後升官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是A-LAWS的精英  很可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死了自己的父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親在協助叛亂分子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在遵守軍紀而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道是父親還開槍的嗎  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了期待著消除紛爭的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違背軍紀  給政權造成威脅的人必須被處決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少由親人來送他上路  這也算是我的憐憫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種  這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的情況下  你會怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人的生命就能輕易奪去  而親人就做不到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死父親的男人和想為家人報仇的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重視她的話  你就去守護她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準尉  我們是在為理想而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此也會有必須下決斷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遲早也會遇到這種局面的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我能做到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向沙慈開槍這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帶回露易絲·哈萊維的話只能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要帶回她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍終於也歸A-LAWS管轄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅在這四個月內 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS就發動了二十次以上的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們越來越慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這件事  敵人是不是真的能找到我們的位置？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加越來越慘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:14:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·諾瑞加  看來還是應該實行那項作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那項作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是吠陀  聯邦…不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者們通過吠陀來進行情報管制這點應該錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要奪回了吠陀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是關鍵在於不知道吠陀的位置的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也無從下手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能從知道情報的人那裡問了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  難道去問改革者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  萊爾  能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼他的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從中學起就去念寄宿學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要去寄宿學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不想跟能幹的哥哥比較
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起戰鬥  我選擇了逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你跟你哥哥一樣  成為了Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動機不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來我還沒問過  亞琉你的家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想說的話就別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你現在能在這裡  這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉  亞琉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在正在接吻的時候發呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向艦隊報告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是李維夫  鼻子跟狗一樣靈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在感謝你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼迪有聯絡來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  把航向轉到普特利麥奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李拜巴爾上尉來電
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現Celestial Being  位置在ES8874
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓MS隊出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓有特權的那兩個人協助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊準備出擊  MS隊準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能駕駛AHEAD了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機能沒有異常  GN-Drive開始接入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艙門開啟 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會戰鬥的  要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD第一小隊  出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  哈萊維機  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體的整備很完美  你所說的奧義也能更進一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話不用說全了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了然於心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學攝影機拍攝到MS隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距到達戰鬥空域還有0054
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之說來說去就拜託像平常那樣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…米蕾娜  你情緒太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  肩膀情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在捕捉到A-LAWS的MS十二台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量意外的少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的部隊裡有改革者的專用機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的部隊裡有路易絲的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這四個月來  你們雖然為了重整戰力一直在逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  已經又要戰鬥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:18:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要對路易絲開槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  要看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥並不只是破壞  也能夠孕育
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信著  我們Gundam能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的  就看你了
